title: Egg Free Chocolate Cake
ingredients: ['110g butter', '250g caster sugar', '120ml milk', '350g smooth apple sauce', '2 tablespoons dark rum', '250g plain flour', '20g unsweetened cocoa', '2 teaspoons bicarbonate of soda', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1 teaspoon ground nutmeg', '1/8 teaspoon salt', '150g sultanas or raisins', '125g chopped pecans', '60ml dark rum']
